Facebook Must Face Privacy Suit Over Giving Advertisers Users’ Information

-- B y   J o e l   R o s e n b l a t t
-- 
2011-05-13T01:15:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-13/facebook-must-face-privacy-suit-over-giving-advertisers-users-information.html
Facebook Inc. must face a privacy
lawsuit over sharing users’ identification with advertisers, a
judge ruled, dismissing some of the claims against the social
networking site.  To contact the reporter on this story:
